{"tid":736572,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好耐冇見過星星","createTime":"2018-07-10T10:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T16:26:30.000Z","uid":31181,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4ac785ef8253a99bee22acfc371fb683869f8d","tid":736572,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"以家身處外國<br />\n頭先見到天到有幾粒光點<br />\n以為係飛機<br />\n抬高頭一睇 原來有勁多粒 先醒起係星星<br />\n好似書入面話漆黑入面嘅螢火蟲咁<br />\n望住個天 個感覺好陌生<br />\n對上個次係香港見到星星<br />\n好似好耐之前<br />\n我覺得好慚愧<br />\n第一時間諗起竟然係人造飛機 而唔係大自然嘅星星"},{"pid":"d60850ff907ef0c865a431d93b494656bd830712","tid":736572,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60d004d1e2df50bbf8d72f974df732365e1e2f09","tid":736572,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"去野外露宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e51c0e9c81ba17724a186a26e94a556edf3b5","tid":736572,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d004d1e2df50bbf8d72f974df732365e1e2f09","tid":736572,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"去野外露宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"有冇介紹？"},{"pid":"52d322af4dd8a78f4706cc4208bd8841800b4eb9","tid":736572,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱先見完，又話好耐無見，講大話唔貶眼"},{"pid":"0f9cde79480a5a0f549a5dd9b0c9dd47d89c8f7e","tid":736572,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"211e51c0e9c81ba17724a186a26e94a556edf3b5","tid":736572,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d004d1e2df50bbf8d72f974df732365e1e2f09","tid":736572,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"去野外露宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"